<hr width=75%>
PROTEIN-DNA BINDING DATA

<ul> 
<li> Binding matrix from Genome-Wide Location Analysis <br><br>
     in vivo for 6870 yeast intergenic regions, 206 transcription factors  <br>
     from Harbison <i> et al </i>, Transcriptional regulatory code of a eukaryotic genome. Nature <b> 431 </b>, 99 (2004). 
     <a href="http://web.wi.mit.edu/young/regulatory_code/"> download data </a>  <br> <br>
     in vitro for 6723 yeast intergenic regions, 3 transcription factors (Abf1,Rap1 and Mig1)  <br>
     from Mukherjee <i> et al </i>, Rapid Analysis of the DNA Binding Specificities of Transcription Factors with DNA Microarrays. Nature Genetics<b> 36 </b>, 1331 (2004). 
     <a href="http://the_brain.bwh.harvard.edu/NatGenet2004_Suppl/Supplementary_Data.htm"> download data </a>  <br>
</ul>

